# Never pack upstream consumer-owned / local project artifacts into the npm tarball.
# Installer seeds fresh empty MEMORY.md + stack.md for new consumers and preserves existing ones.
# Note: presence of this file means npm does NOT apply root .gitignore — list bytecode/junk here too.

.agents/skills/shared/config.json
.agents/skills/shared/config.local.json
.agents/skills/shared/stack.md
.agents/skills/shared/MEMORY.md
.agents/skills/shared/memory/**
!.agents/skills/shared/MEMORY.md.template
!.agents/skills/shared/stack.md.example
!.agents/skills/shared/config.json.example

**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
